  "texts": [
    "Subtasks are dependent and will be executed in serial order with a single agent.We use an example to illustrate the decomposition process.",
    "If the task of analyzing vehicle weight and fuel efficiency is completed with a score of 6/10, the agent might suggest the following decompositions: T1: Segment the data into weight categories (light, medium, heavy) and analyze the fuel efficiency within each segment.",
    "T2: Within each weight category, conduct a clustering analysis to identify patterns or groupings that could further explain variations in fuel efficiency.",
    "T3: Perform a multiple regression analysis to control for additional variables like engine size and vehicle age.",
    "The execution logic would be (T1 DOWN T2 AND T3).According to the logic, the agent executes each subtask and summarizes the subtasks' insights to formulate an overall insight for the decomposed task."
  ],
